Package: rubrica-associati
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Meskatech <276923+meska@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: libgtk-3-0 | libgtk-3-0t64, libglib2.0-0, libstdc++6
Description: private offline member directory for community groups
 Manages members, cards, expiry dates and contacts locally, with Excel and CSV
 import. It does not require an account, server or Internet connection.
